      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true automotive time capsule. This vehicle is in breathtaking, showroom condition, having been meticulously garaged and climate-controlled since day one. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with a professional ceramic coating, showing absolutely no chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in a factory-fresh state; the premium leather seats are supple with zero bolster wear, and every button retains its original tactile crispness. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, backed by a comprehensive binder of every service interval performed at the original dealership. This is not just a used car; it is a meticulously preserved specimen for the most discerning collector. Includes all original keys, manuals, and a clean title in hand.",
