      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home. This car is in absolutely stunning, mint condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just left the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it spotless and garage-kept. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for your next big adventure. If you're looking for something that's been loved and kept in perfect shape, you just found it! Feel free to reach out if you want to come take a look!",
